  "3061380": {
    "name": "Devive",
    "steam_appid": 3061380,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/53d24e2274e0827df3303d883c5abaa5.avif?t=1767609055\" width=800 height=300 /></span><strong><i>Discover the first game from a friendly team that brings together video game graduate students, young teachers and industry veterans.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DEVIVE is an action-adventure game where your life is constantly decreasing. Run into a race against death to bring your child back to life, drain the energy of your enemies to survive, unlock skills to forge your fighting style, and solve a variety of puzzles to harvest the power of a fallen entity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/6bbe70ccdf39019336c3718ff8ae888e.avif?t=1767609055\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Saïka, a young mother determined to bring her child back to life</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/0f1f7fd7450e364051ffe5dde964b65c.webp?t=1767609055\" width=616 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drain the energy of organic enemies to stay alive while your life is constantly decreasing. When you dominate an organic enemy, the properties of your attacks change. Use this mechanic to gain an advantage during encounters.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/076088f01ccf488b5f4d05ae678320d2.poster.avif?t=1767609055\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/076088f01ccf488b5f4d05ae678320d2.webm?t=1767609055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/076088f01ccf488b5f4d05ae678320d2.mp4?t=1767609055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/ac505ddfbcdde131330358ef1071e1bd.webp?t=1767609055\" width=616 height=27 /></span>Also face forged golems to repel anyone who covets Talakti's power. Combat is fast-paced and based primarily on ranged attacks and unique skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/f7cee143d49539a02334c50b04a21687.poster.avif?t=1767609055\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/f7cee143d49539a02334c50b04a21687.webm?t=1767609055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/f7cee143d49539a02334c50b04a21687.mp4?t=1767609055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environmental secrets and puzzles are the key to progress and to reaping the power of a fallen and once-enslaved entity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/7a2f62c682eb9fac34485e67fc5c63bb.poster.avif?t=1767609055\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/7a2f62c682eb9fac34485e67fc5c63bb.webm?t=1767609055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/7a2f62c682eb9fac34485e67fc5c63bb.mp4?t=1767609055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/03a98bf817ad107584779be3052ad600.webp?t=1767609055\" width=616 height=27 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize gameplay by unlocking a variety of skills affecting your fighting style, drain efficiency, mobility and vitality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/9c91e20067fe1d158d0f3349db00fb10.avif?t=1767609055\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras_big/9c91e20067fe1d158d0f3349db00fb10.webp?t=1767609055 width=1560 height=886 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/71dc7b7779b1ff2886c53c079d259594.avif?t=1767609055\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by games like <i>Shadow of the Colossus</i>, DEVIVE tells the story of Saïka, a young mother seeking the power of Talakti, a fallen entity to bring her child back to life. It's up to you to explore the scene of a cursed place and piece together the drama that unfolded there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/d1ad4db0f2c1bf4252c2cdb4b6160efd.avif?t=1767609055\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras_big/d1ad4db0f2c1bf4252c2cdb4b6160efd.webp?t=1767609055 width=1560 height=882 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/ad48660eede3f3fd0922cb572d183e0f.avif?t=1767609055\" width=800 height=300 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 to 5 hours of play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast and dynamic combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A skill system to customize your fighting style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied environmental puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Levels that are sometimes challenging but not punitive.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Narrative collectibles to recreate the game’s story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two different endings.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>We hope DEVIVE will give you an unforgettable experience.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thank you for being part of our adventure.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061380/extras/c92f72513b343bfda0e662e9059b057e.avif?t=1767609055\" width=500 height=300 /></span></p>",
